{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}
Since acceding to the throne of [[Sweden]] in 1973, [[Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden|King Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden]] has received a number of state and official visits.<ref name="royalsweden"/> He usually hosts one or two visiting heads of state each year.
